race.comment: UNCONVICTED (2) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a neck (26.32) behind Ayla Zorro at this track. Can find winning form. VISTA YANK (3) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 461m behind Times Flying (26.38) in a Special conditions race. Deserves plenty of respect. ONE MORE CAKE (1) is on a hot streak of form, jumping from this box to score last time at this track (26.45), making it two straight wins. Has the ability and looks a key chance. SPARE A DIME (4) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.
